preview.html: A kiss on the neck in a single woman’s dream is among the visions that carry a lot of interpretation, which is determined depending on the person who kisses the dreamer, as well as the condition of the dreamer in the dream. To a job that has authority and high status and he will get money from it. It will change her living conditions for the better. If an unmarried woman sees being kissed on the neck by someone she knows, this means that the engagement date of the visionary is approaching and she will be engaged to someone she loves and loves and will live a happy married life with him. Whereas if an unmarried woman sees that a stranger kissed her on the neck against her will One of the dreams that warns that the woman in the vision will be exposed to many obstacles and problems as a result of her engagement to an inappropriate man. And she will suffer a lot with him until this engagement is canceled. It is obligatory for him to honor his parents, teacher, emigrate, visit a scholar, or perform a pilgrimage. To perform their religion: Whoever performs Hajj and does not perform any of the acts of Hajj, then he goes to the Sultan for his need.
